    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我在床上翻来覆去，被窗外的雨声吵得睡不着。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "大概真的有“假期后综合征”这回事，从海岛回来之后，我时常觉得睡不踏实。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-1",
        "Flag": "b-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "b-1-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "打开窗户",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "凉爽的空气夹着潮湿气息，一下子涌入房间，稍稍缓解了我的烦躁。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "昨天公司刚通知近期将有异常天气，接着就连下了两天的大雨。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不过这会儿我倒想起了另一件事。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "（下雨……对了，天台上的那些植物……）",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "春天快要过去的时候，不知是谁在天台一角辟出了一块花圃。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "花圃中栽上了些从未见过的幼苗，稀疏而卷曲的叶片柔软地匍匐在地上。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "起初我没在意，只是偶尔瞥见那些叶片渐渐舒展开来，像是适应了新的环境，枝茎也慢慢长高。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一个夏天过去，交叠的绿叶之间已经冒出几粒莹白花芽，散发出令人舒服的气味。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不知不觉，我开始期待花朵盛开的样子，工作间隙也总爱去天台逛逛。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "也不知道天台的花怎么样了，即便植物需要灌溉，恐怕也难以承受这接连的大雨。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这么想着，窗外的雨声渐渐小了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "反正已经睡不着，索性去天台散散心吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "雨已经停了，月亮格外皎洁，将天台地面照出一汪汪清亮。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "还没看到花圃，先闻见一阵幽香，在雨后的夜晚氤氲着扩散。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "清新而甜美的气味，既是花香，又像是谁身上的味道，向着我缓缓聚拢。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "？？？",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这么巧！是你呀。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就在我想起这香味来源的同一时间，熟悉的声音也在身后响起。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她的味道比她的声音更早被我察觉，转过身，许久未见的倩影立在夜色里。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "随即，她小步向我跑来，柔白色的衣裙也跟着一颤一颤。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "克罗瑞娜病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "晚上好，playername。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
